@startuml
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEF5FF
  BorderColor #4A78B5
}

title ERC-8183 Agentic Commerce — Job State Machine

[*] --> Open : client creates job
Open --> Funded : client funds escrow
Open --> Rejected : client rejects (while Open)
Funded --> Submitted : provider submits work
Funded --> Rejected : evaluator rejects (before submission)
Submitted --> Completed : evaluator attests completion
Submitted --> Rejected : evaluator rejects
Funded --> Refunded : job expires
Completed --> [*]
Rejected --> [*]
Refunded --> [*]

note right of Completed
  Only the evaluator may
  mark a job Completed.
  Optional reason hash
  composes with ERC-8004
  reputation.
end note

@enduml
